{"ja428:0.1":"Jataka ","ja428:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja428:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja428:0.4":"2. Kosambiyajataka ","ja428:1.1":"“Puthusaddo samajano, ","ja428:1.2":"na balo koci mannatha; ","ja428:1.3":"Sanghasmim bhijjamanasmim, ","ja428:1.4":"nannam bhiyyo amannarum. ","ja428:2.1":"Parimuttha panditabhasa, ","ja428:2.2":"vacagocarabhanino; ","ja428:2.3":"Yavicchanti mukhayamam, ","ja428:2.4":"yena nita na tam vidu. ","ja428:3.1":"Akkocchi mam avadhi mam, ","ja428:3.2":"ajini mam ahasi me; ","ja428:3.3":"Ye ca tam upanayhanti, ","ja428:3.4":"veram tesam na sammati. ","ja428:4.1":"Akkocchi mam avadhi mam, ","ja428:4.2":"ajini mam ahasi me; ","ja428:4.3":"Ye ca tam nupanayhanti, ","ja428:4.4":"veram tesupasammati. ","ja428:5.1":"Na hi verena verani, ","ja428:5.2":"sammantidha kudacanam; ","ja428:5.3":"Averena ca sammanti, ","ja428:5.4":"esa dhammo sanantano. ","ja428:6.1":"Pare ca na vijananti, ","ja428:6.2":"mayamettha yamamase; ","ja428:6.3":"Ye ca tattha vijananti, ","ja428:6.4":"tato sammanti medhaga. ","ja428:7.1":"Atthicchinna panahara, ","ja428:7.2":"gavassa dhanaharino; ","ja428:7.3":"Rattham vilumpamananam, ","ja428:7.4":"tesampi hoti sangati; ","ja428:7.5":"Kasma tumhaka no siya. ","ja428:8.1":"Sace labhetha nipakam sahayam, ","ja428:8.2":"Saddhim caram sadhuviharidhiram; ","ja428:8.3":"Abhibhuyya sabbani parissayani, ","ja428:8.4":"Careyya tenattamano satima. ","ja428:9.1":"No ce labhetha nipakam sahayam, ","ja428:9.2":"Saddhim caram sadhuviharidhiram; ","ja428:9.3":"Rajava rattham vijitam pahaya, ","ja428:9.4":"Eko care matangaranneva nago. ","ja428:10.1":"Ekassa caritam seyyo, ","ja428:10.2":"Natthi bale sahayata; ","ja428:10.3":"Eko care na papani kayira, ","ja428:10.4":"Appossukko matangaranneva nago”ti. ","ja428:11.1":"Kosambiyajatakam dutiyam. "}